{"tid":466443,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"有無人同我一樣 都係到等緊一個人？","createTime":"2017-11-12T14:34:34.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-15T04:01:34.000Z","uid":79663,"like":53,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"478cde8e3784bcf5d9672067f1b97121c10a26e9","tid":466443,"uid":79663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-12T14:34:34.000Z","msg":"每一日起身第一件事就係拎起電話 睇你有無揾我 係我每一日嘅動力同期待<br />\n我話我會等你 其實我都唔知最後等唔等到個結果<br />\n我唔知要等幾耐 或者悲觀d咁講 除咗等之外我冇嘢可以做<br />\n<br />\n仲記得啱啱識你個陣 大家都話覺得 揾到一個人靜靜地陪住自己已經好夠<br />\n第一次見面 就算沉默都唔會覺得尷尬<br />\n就係個日 我覺得我終於揾到我塊碎片<br />\n <br />\n我地都鍾意藍色 正確黎講係深籃色<br />\n我：你睇 係你啱啱話個本書呀！有我鍾意嘅藍色<br />\n你：係我鍾意嘅藍色<br />\n我：係我。。<br />\n你：係。。<br />\n（我：係我鍾意嘅你 鍾意嘅藍色）<br />\n個陣嘅我仲未有勇氣講出口<br />\n<br />\n個日我地係海旁 你攬住我 一齊聽住歌<br />\n好想個一刻可以永遠停留<br />\n我唔知道上世嘅我 究竟做左幾多好事 先可以今世遇到你<br />\n我淨係知我唔想錯過你<br />\n<br />\n你話你驚<br />\n我好想比勇氣你 好想你可以信任我<br />\n如果可以 我好想可以重新黎過<br />\n我會大大力攬住你 同你講 ych我愛你<br />\n無論係用咩身份 我都希望可以永遠留係你身邊。。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span style=\"color: pink;\">你肯揾我未呀？<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </span> </span>"},{"pid":"ac6c80faabb6d9e190d4c8b3a97c03a6a09407fc","tid":466443,"uid":21423,"like":1,"dislike":7,"score":-6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-12T14:37:38.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"374539313e180a12e2d1f85d5484a7cae9754cdb","tid":466443,"uid":55505,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-12T14:45:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nI know that feel bro<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/12/224454_2041338bf107a6e1ae8e33b326767839.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F12%2F224454_2041338bf107a6e1ae8e33b326767839.jpg&h=0d4727f0&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"eba61b5e7ef163386e40fbb4fec5a5750877d6d1","tid":466443,"uid":3908,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-12T14:50:19.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"74537279ab8750fba47ae68d59a8abb72ccf3626","tid":466443,"uid":20867,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-12T14:58:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nI know that feel bro<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/12/224454_2041338bf107a6e1ae8e33b326767839.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F12%2F224454_2041338bf107a6e1ae8e33b326767839.jpg&h=0d4727f0&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n人同人既相識冥冥中有安排同理由<br />\n但結果唔一定系發展成情侶／夫妻"},{"pid":"d2d7ed4eb0a1388afab286b5074ef02d8fe21e99","tid":466443,"uid":79663,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-13T01:28:30.000Z","msg":"未關係你也不用給我機會 反正我還有一生可以浪費"},{"pid":"da9c90273c43b3e7ce2598c1450ad82ae3a04828","tid":466443,"uid":59379,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-13T01:48:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>未關係你也不用給我機會 反正我還有一生可以浪費</blockquote><br />\n出到呢首。。。<br />\n無機會追到喇咩？"},{"pid":"d47952d33a7396bab1d078df94ad2fc4c83dfecf","tid":466443,"uid":27708,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-13T02:03:55.000Z","msg":"係咪俾帽人呀"},{"pid":"9fa4000714c36f240db9dcc5e5bd953a59941f10","tid":466443,"uid":144913,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-13T03:25:07.000Z","msg":"我block左佢whatsapp ig，我心底裹好怕佢搵返我，佢傷得我好深，我明知一切已經變哂。<br />\n<br />\n佢變左心，我俾佢hurt到性格、心態、思想都變埋，我想做返以前嘅我，身邊有好多fd勸過我，開解我，俾正能量我，但解鈴還須繫鈴人，我一直接受唔到其他人，好多野只係想同佢做，完全唔想俾其他人取代到佢個位，完全冇俾過機會其他人，只係好想返到去以前同佢簡單開心就夠<br />\n<br />\n我唔知我咁樣算唔算叫做等緊佢"},{"pid":"0695ca977ee82752fed0c265f08fb234e6de67a0","tid":466443,"uid":137847,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-13T05:11:58.000Z","msg":"等緊佢.....唉"},{"pid":"b6293788e4b19b6005cdcf85502e2f8d108be5fd","tid":466443,"uid":101804,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-13T06:17:22.000Z","msg":"等個仆佳幾時死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 同完佢一個共同朋友食飯先知佢吹水吹到飛起，咩入chanel扮買袋，扮有錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 吹水吹到話跪係到喊唔好分手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 好彩人地都有腦，再比埋啲證據人睇先知佢有幾柒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 屌佢老母犯眾憎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6683bd1490a09e535025234bb6a7bccde5b73976","tid":466443,"uid":10084,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-13T06:30:54.000Z","msg":"等左七年<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n完"},{"pid":"7a403a29a223d0da62b9ee822f83acefecf1a4e8","tid":466443,"uid":79663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-13T10:27:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>係咪俾帽人呀</blockquote><br />\n佢之前被帽過 好大打擊"},{"pid":"50a24911575837eb64bcb5142f28746abe9a65ab","tid":466443,"uid":79663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-13T10:30:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>未關係你也不用給我機會 反正我還有一生可以浪費</blockquote><br />\n出到呢首。。。<br />\n無機會追到喇咩？</blockquote><br />\n佢已讀不回<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 打比佢又好似太chur。。"},{"pid":"14180314e164b29120b569d000d79136fdefa6b4","tid":466443,"uid":156849,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-13T10:32:00.000Z","msg":"人地而家已經拍緊拖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，等佢有一日可能會分手，不過呢一種等唔知等到幾時<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a87aeddf6d83a67290ea2c254baaee41533d82d1","tid":466443,"uid":54927,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-13T10:33:51.000Z","msg":"垃圾"},{"pid":"50583bc270369e208209fc883bdaff4480f596fe","tid":466443,"uid":135390,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-13T11:11:39.000Z","msg":"等緊一個突破口<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n不過冇你咁close,未攬過,乜都冇做過,淨係wts"},{"pid":"0887e51d70d93a1ef938c696ea545143ed674d49","tid":466443,"uid":15454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-13T11:18:31.000Z","msg":"Same<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唔知幾時先等到你翻黎我身邊"},{"pid":"301ebbccfdd2b79a44538fdda131caa192ac822f","tid":466443,"uid":79663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-13T14:10:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>等緊一個突破口<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n不過冇你咁close,未攬過,乜都冇做過,淨係wts</blockquote><br />\n佢知唔知你鍾意佢？佢對你有無feel？"},{"pid":"a1d84a2604b55a8a4933cf209605a7972e15ee61","tid":466443,"uid":157550,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-13T14:22:58.000Z","msg":"佢前排已經調左舖去左第到做 冇對方contact 因為我淆底唔敢問<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/16.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n跟住上個星期佢無啦啦返黎探返我地 我已經開心到癲左 雖然佢唔會睇得出<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n同佢相處真係好舒服好開心 <br />\n自此之後我返工既動力就係等佢再返黎搵我同班同事<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/want_die.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n每次返工都係度期待佢會黎 <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/want_die.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n其實我唔奢望會我地會有咩關係 佢已經有女朋友 <br />\n但我忘記唔到佢 自從佢走左後 我就冇晚訓得好 好掛住佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/want_die.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5cb771ba16c78744a928d652e5db65d974343090","tid":466443,"uid":111811,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-13T14:30:55.000Z","msg":"如果人地有對象<br />\n應該等待定放手<br />\n定順其自然"},{"pid":"d3ee6e5273a12824a5b7f9c23e9a9a4b31054a99","tid":466443,"uid":26401,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-13T14:55:17.000Z","msg":"我都係等緊一個人。我同第二個男仔爭緊佢，佢話對我同第二個男仔都有心動過所以做唔到個選擇。但我係街撞見佢同第二個男仔既時候，我個心真係好撚痛。雖然佢都有同我約會，一齊行街睇戲食飯吹海風，但係佢平時又鍾意唔覆我啲whatsapp。我成日覺得好似自己已經輸撚左咁，日日都提心吊膽。我真係好唔捨得佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n利申：等佢覆我whatsapp等左成日"},{"pid":"798354c7f36afa38629d708903b5982d1149be5a","tid":466443,"uid":156849,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-13T15:01:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>如果人地有對象<br />\n應該等待定放手<br />\n定順其自然</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n唉順其自然啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"004bb4189186bddd7f8f9eaffc64d95e9f5dc439","tid":466443,"uid":55505,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-13T15:16:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>如果人地有對象<br />\n應該等待定放手<br />\n定順其自然</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n唉順其自然啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n令到佢個對象變你自己<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6de0f4fb4e0fa601e34bd049dc4629249d82cbd1","tid":466443,"uid":79663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-13T15:55:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>如果人地有對象<br />\n應該等待定放手<br />\n定順其自然</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n唉順其自然啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n令到佢個對象變你自己<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n有時會想主動爭取 覺得太被動會錯失機會 有時又覺得要順其自然 因為機會係留比有機會嘅人<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}